cast.overview: Members of the Granite Mountain Hotshots battle deadly wildfires to save an Arizona town.
cast.title: Only the Brave

details.biography: Raleigh was born in Kansas City, MO and raised in the vast plains of Kansas. It was there that her love for playing pretend grew. She is known for The Night Shift (2014) , Longmire (2012) , and Manhattan (2014) . Raleigh became involved in musical theater at her high school and went on to training in theater for a short time at Loyola Marymount University in Los Angeles. After deciding to take a break from acting, she finished her bachelor's degree in Elementary Education in Kansas. Raleigh currently writes, acts, and runs in Los Angeles.
details.name: Raleigh Cain
